eplyTime":"2021-05-05T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"7c1d87b597fd1ccde82ad5e8c16cbce6d5914b08","tid":2517650,"uid":254450,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23ff7fcbdd70233bd7da8f027f08574fb13c0a9b","tid":2517650,"uid":43178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"Apple 出咗隻字體有香港版，叫蘋方-香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkfW2w5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkfW2w5.png&h=7648acdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"雨體食讀都唔香港wor<br />\n<br />\n雨應該係四點都向右下<br />\n體個骨字細個寫開T骨<br />\n食字人下面係點唔係橫，下面果忽係痴埋<br />\n讀字入面果個唔係四字係目字打橫<br />\n<br />\n呢隻已經係台灣騎劫版香港字體，憑咩叫自己香港字體"},{"pid":"6f81287a6f00ebeda57ee0ff0224979d08b21cb2","tid":2517650,"uid":175732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n以前呢D野老師都唔撚會理"}]}